<div dir="ltr"><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">Hello Folks!</font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">We’ve seen a couple of deployments pop up over the last few weeks to help map the Nigerian General Elections. Olu and his team at Connected Development (CODE) have been working on Uzabe – <a href="https://uzabe.crowdmap.com/" rel="nofollow" style="text-decoration:none">https://uzabe.crowdmap.com</a> and need some help around Reports management and Geolocation.</font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">They’ve done a good job outlining what <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1x43WFPy3WD6a8QFVMHzAbCFzisYool6OeR-Gw8evI28/edit#slide=id.p3" style="text-decoration:none">their workflow is here</a></font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">If you’re interested in volunteering, <a href="http://goo.gl/forms/db0KCrnhvG" style="text-decoration:none">please sign up on this volunteer form</a></font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">For some context, those who would be interested in working on the Geolocation team would be helping out with ensuring report/incidents are tagged to correct locations as accurately as possible. The Uzabe team has developed a <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1x43WFPy3WD6a8QFVMHzAbCFzisYool6OeR-Gw8evI28/edit#slide=id.p3" style="text-decoration:none">Polling Unit Location guide for this</a>.</font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">For those who would be interested in helping with categorization, verification and approval of reports, <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QCBdGg5tJqSXGqN7tdQwdahgM9wjS3pCzU2f3sN9CNo/edit#gid=965144712" style="text-decoration:none">here is their category checklist </a>.</font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><font color="#000000">For more context on the work his team is doing, here is a link to the <a href="http://bit.ly/uzabeplanning" style="text-decoration:none">Uzabe planning document</a></font></p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif">Have a great weekend!</p><p style="font-size:13px;margin:0.7em 0px;padding:0px;line-height:18.2000007629395px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif"><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136);font-family:arial,sans-serif;font-size:small;line-height:normal">-- </span></p><div class="gmail_signature"><div dir="ltr"><div><div dir="ltr"><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136)">Angela Oduor Lungati.</span><br style="color:rgb(136,136,136)"><a href="http://ushahidi.com/" style="color:rgb(17,85,204)" target="_blank">Ushahidi Inc</a><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136)">.</span><br style="color:rgb(136,136,136)"><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136)">Platforms: </span><a href="http://download.ushahidi.com/" style="color:rgb(17,85,204)" target="_blank">Ushahidi</a><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136)"> | </span><a href="https://crowdmap.com/" style="color:rgb(17,85,204)" target="_blank">Crowdmap</a><span style="color:rgb(136,136,136)"> | </span><a href="ht